        <h2>Why Proper Electrical Work Matters</h2>
        <p>Electrical problems are not just inconvenient -- they can be dangerous. Faulty wiring is one of the leading causes of house fires in the United States. Homes with outdated aluminum wiring, ungrounded outlets, or overloaded circuits carry elevated risk that a professional inspection can identify before it becomes an emergency.</p>
        <p>Utah's building codes exist to protect homeowners, and every repair or installation Osborne Electric performs meets or exceeds current NEC and local code requirements. We pull permits when required, schedule inspections, and stand behind every connection we make.</p>
